2. Background
=============

There are two different components to a complete build pipeline.
There is the CI (Continuous Integration) and CD (Continuous Delievery).
In CI, you have the concept of developers, Source code repositories and various types of build and testing infrastructures.
In the CD space, one usually has a system keep track of servers, a master server to push instructions to infrastructure and so on.

In CI, the source code repository, generally they have a basic version controllable ability
